@startuml
title Finance Tooling - Full Corpus Workflow

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontName Courier

start

:Load settings from env/.env;
:Resolve input/output/category/fx paths;

:Discover all statement PDFs recursively;
:Prepare extraction (cache hit/miss) and parser selection diagnostics;
:Parse all discovered statements;

if (HSBC CSV path configured?) then (yes)
  :Discover HSBC CSV files;
  :Import CSV transactions;
  :Map CSV rows to statement months via parsed period windows;
  :Adaptive month selection\n(CSV vs PDF by reconciliation mismatch);
endif

:Merge selected parsed transactions;
:Run categorization\n(rules -> overrides -> fallback);
:Apply FX conversion and source-file mtime enrichment;

:Compute completeness report and reconciliation metrics;
:Upsert canonical transactions into master parquet;
:Export normalized CSV + JSON;
:Render dashboard HTML;
:Write run_summary.json and completeness_report.json;

if (Guardrail violations and strict mode?) then (yes)
  :Return non-zero exit code;
else (no)
  :Return success;
endif

stop
@enduml
